**Workflow:**
User -> Planner;
Planner -> WebSearcher;
WebSearcher -> Summarizer;
Summarizer -> End.

**Description:**
1. Planner formulates a three-phase strategy: initial keyword filtering, secondary content scanning, and tertiary full-text validation.
2. WebSearcher executes boolean searches, accesses full-text content via multiple databases, and systematically verifies exclusion criteria across all sections.
3. Summarizer cross-validates findings against exclusion terms, checks supplementary materials, and ensures proper compound naming.
